data.description: Welcome to 6907 Pegram Way, a charming and spacious home nestled on a quiet cul-de-sac in a desirable neighborhood. This beautiful property offers a perfect blend of comfort, style, and functionality.  As you step inside, you are greeted by a bright and inviting living area, perfect for entertaining guests or relaxing with family. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living room to the dining area and kitchen, creating a warm and inclusive atmosphere. The kitchen boasts modern appliances, ample counter space, and plenty of storage. The adjacent dining area features large windows that flood the space with natural light, creating a delightful ambiance for meals. The main floor is completed with powder room, laundry, and primary bedroom with en-suite bathroom. The main living area flows into the upstairs bonus area loft, adjacent to two bedrooms, each offering walk-in closet. A peaceful retreat for rest and relaxation. The lower level has a spacious entertainment area, full bath, the fourth bedroom with egress and walk in closet, and a large utility area with storage. The backyard has a spacious 16'x20' patio area perfect for outdoor dining and entertaining. 6907 Pegram Way is conveniently located near schools, parks, shopping centers, and major transportation routes, making it an ideal location for families and commuters alike. Sellers giving a carpet allowance and a home warranty.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home. Schedule a showing today and experience the charm.
